original_title: The Life and Legacy of Dr. Susan La Flesche Picotte
overview: This short documentary tells the story of the life and legacy of Dr. Susan La Flesche Picotte, an Omaha woman who became the first Native American physician.

production_companies.name: The Nebraska Commission on Indian Affairs

tagline: “I shall always fight good and hard, even if I have to fight alone.”
title: The Life and Legacy of Dr. Susan La Flesche Picotte
